          <title>
            <string language="en">Women and Economic Empowerment</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Frauen und ökonomische Ermächtigung</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Femmes et habilitation économique</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Mulheres e empowerment econômico</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Donne ed empowerment economico</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Γυναίκες και οικονομική ενδυνάμωση</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Mujeres y empowerment económico</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">The purpose of this lesson is to acquaint students with historic and current-day factors that impact women's economic status. </string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Humanities</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <coverage>
            <string language="en">North America</string>
          </coverage>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Der Zweck dieser Lektion ist, Kursteilnehmer mit 
den historischen und Aktuelltagfaktoren mitzuteilen, die ökonomischen
Status der Frauen auswirken.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Le but de cette leçon est de mettre au courant 
des étudiants des facteurs historiques et d'actuel-jour qui 
effectuent le mode économique des femmes.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">A finalidade desta lição é familiarizar 
estudantes com os fatores historic e de atual-dia que impactam o 
status econômico das mulheres.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Lo scopo di questa lezione è informare gli 
allievi dei fattori di corrente-giorno e storici che hanno effetto 
sulla condizione economica delle donne.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Ο σκοπός αυτού του μαθήματος είναι να εξοικειωθούν οι
σπουδαστές με τους ιστορικούς και παράγοντες παρών-ημέρας που 
επηρεάζουν την οικονομική θέση των γυναικών.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">El propósito de esta lección es conocer a 
estudiantes de los factores históricos y del actual-di'a que afectan 
el estatus económico de las mujeres.</string>
          </description>
